messages.content: My status is good, Tally. Ready to complete the mission and serve our faction with honor. How about you?
messages.speaker: Evripidis Xenakis

messages.content: I'm currently unarmed, Tally. My role is to provide support and backup for the rest of the team. Are you carrying your autorifle?
messages.speaker: Evripidis Xenakis

messages.content: Excellent, Tally. Your autorifle will definitely come in handy during this mission. Have you checked your equipment and ammunition to make sure everything is in order?
messages.speaker: Evripidis Xenakis

messages.content: I said, have you checked your equipment and ammunition to make sure everything is in order, Tally? It's important to make sure we're all prepared for what's ahead.
